metadata.name: [art]ificial #1
metadata.description:
This is [art]ificial #1 by Pixedelic.

[art]ificial work is proteiform, born from legacy art augmented with AI and hand made scripts.

The idea behind [art]ificial is to create images with extended perspectives to dive into unique fantasy and sci-fi atmospheres. There is no given interpretation, each of us can feel it and see something different.

The Artificial Intelligence (AI) used for this generative art is a next generation algorithm, capable of creating astonishing images with no artefact.

My inspiration comes from many artists, including :
 - Comics masters : Philippe Druillet and Jack Kirby
 - Famous painters : Gustave Dore and Fernand Leger
 - And many unkown street artists 

Resolution : 4000 x 4000 px
